name: Cyber Clutch: Hot Import Nights - Overdrive Pack
summary: Embrace the future of racing with the 'Hot Import Nights: Cyber Clutch - Overdrive Edition. This exclusive package features two unique car models - the agile Wasp and the sleek Scythe. Each comes with 12 distinctive holographic customization items, available only in this edition.
